org.jooby

Interface Asset


  • public interface Asset
    Usually a public file/resource like javascript, css, images files, etc... An asset consist of content type, stream and last modified since, between others.
    Since:
    0.1.0
    Author:
    edgar
    See Also:
    Jooby.assets(String)
